erusalem-suspect-killed/0000018e-3799-d977-a5ae-7fdd25460000</guid></item><item><title>外交部长称南非将逮捕持有双重国籍的以色列士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/south-africa-to-arrest-israeli-soldiers-holding-dual-citizenship-foreign-minister-says/0000018e-36e3-d0ac-a1cf-3ef7f8650000</link><description>该国外交部长表示，持有以色列和南非双重国籍的以色列国防军士兵将被立即逮捕。以色列军队正在为其他可能效仿的军队做准备</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 11:42:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/south-africa-to-arrest-israeli-soldiers-holding-dual-citizenship-foreign-minister-says/0000018e-36e3-d0ac-a1cf-3ef7f8650000</guid></item><item><title>本格维尔支持枪杀 13 岁巴勒斯坦儿童的警察后，以色列总检察长发出警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-warns-ben-gvir-for-backing-cop-who-killed-13-year-old-palestinian/0000018e-3774-d361-a3de-7775b32a0000</link><description>本-格维尔出现在正在接受调查的警察局，称“英雄”做得堪称典范；总检察长加利·巴哈拉夫-米亚拉：任何干扰案件调查的行为都是非法的</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 11:22:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-warns-ben-gvir-for-backing-cop-who-killed-13-year-old-palestinian/0000018e-3774-d361-a3de-7775b32a0000</guid></item><item><title>美国对以色列实施武器禁运真的能阻止加沙战争吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/would-a-u-s-arms-embargo-on-israel-really-stop-the-war-in-gaza/0000018e-36c2-d8f9-a98e-7ec381950000</link><description>尽管美国政府可以利用一些公共和私人手段来表达对以色列军事行动的不满，但这些手段都不像一些人所说的那么容易。人们担心，孤立可能会进一步加剧以色列和内塔尼亚胡的胆量，并可能给总理带来国内胜利</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 10:11:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/would-a-u-s-arms-embargo-on-israel-really-stop-the-war-in-gaza/0000018e-36c2-d8f9-a98e-7ec381950000</guid></item><item><title>以色列加大与真主党高风险敌对行动的赌注</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-ups-the-ante-in-high-risk-hostilities-with-hezbollah/0000018e-3447-da0e-a78f-fc7ff5510000</link><description>以色列国防军进攻行动扩大到黎巴嫩贝卡谷地 — — 以及真主党的强化反应 — — 使双方更接近一场他们试图避免的战争</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 04:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-ups-the-ante-in-high-risk-hostilities-with-hezbollah/0000018e-3447-da0e-a78f-fc7ff5510000</guid></item><item><title>以色列袭击黎巴嫩南部哈马斯成员身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article-live/aid-trucks-enter-northern-gaza-from-israel-for-first-time-since-war-on-hamas-broke-out/0000018e-35a6-d9f7-a5ee-f7efeae50000</link><description>哈马斯呼吁西岸巴勒斯坦人向圣殿山/阿克萨清真寺进军，与以色列安全部队对峙 ■ 17 岁巴勒斯坦人在西岸检查站持刀刺伤两名以色列人后身亡 ■ 两名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸检查站被以色列国防军炮火打死约旦河西岸城市杰宁和吉瓦特泽耶夫定居点附近的另外两个城市 ■ 德国批准武装部队向加沙空投援助物资</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 02:43:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article-live/aid-trucks-enter-northern-gaza-from-israel-for-first-time-since-war-on-hamas-broke-out/0000018e-35a6-d9f7-a5ee-f7efeae50000</guid></item><item><title>西岸警察局长：大多数关于定居者暴力的投诉都是虚假的，由无政府主义者提出</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-police-chief-most-complaints-of-settler-violence-are-false-filed-by-anarchists/0000018e-34cf-d5ad-addf-7cdff2310000</link><description>议会小组委员会周二召开会议，讨论“活动人士的煽动活动”。地区警察指挥官指责人权组织“声誉受损”</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 23:11:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-police-chief-most-complaints-of-settler-violence-are-false-filed-by-anarchists/0000018e-34cf-d5ad-addf-7cdff2310000</guid></item><item><title>“不可逆转的损害”：以色列火山研究所负责人抗议预算削减计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/irreversible-damage-heads-of-israels-volcani-institute-protest-planned-budget-cuts/0000018e-342c-d5ad-addf-7c3d53b50000</link><description>火山研究所代理所长什穆埃尔·阿苏林 (Shmuel Assouline) 表示，由于提议的削减，该机构已暂停其活动，他警告说，这将导致该研究所关闭、诉讼和损害、正在申请的专利被取消以及其所拥有的知识产权的损失。国家</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 21:24:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/irreversible-damage-heads-of-israels-volcani-institute-protest-planned-budget-cuts/0000018e-342c-d5ad-addf-7c3d53b50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方在东耶路撒冷射杀一名向他们发射烟花的 13 岁青少年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-fatally-shot-a-13-year-old-who-launched-fireworks-at-them-in-east-jerusalem/0000018e-3457-da0e-a78f-fc7f43e80000</link><description>据难民营一名居民称，烟花并非针对军官，也不会对他们构成威胁。国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔在回应这一事件时表示，他向警察对事件的处理“致敬”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 20:35:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-fatally-shot-a-13-year-old-who-launched-fireworks-at-them-in-east-jerusalem/0000018e-3457-da0e-a78f-fc7f43e80000</guid></item><item><title>新的加沙战争是拜登和内塔尼亚胡之间的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-12/ty-article/.highlight/how-biden-and-netanyahu-conveniently-blame-each-other-for-their-gaza-war-failures/0000018e-33e4-d9f7-a5ee-f7ef84670000</link><description>传统观点认为，比比与拜登关系的恶化对两位领导人来说都是一个糟糕的发展。但真的是这样吗？在每种情况下，爆发相互批评和指责也是有好处的</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 19:46:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-12/ty-article/.highlight/how-biden-and-netanyahu-conveniently-blame-each-other-for-their-gaza-war-failures/0000018e-33e4-d9f7-a5ee-f7ef84670000</guid></item><item><title>希伯来大学停职否认哈马斯性暴力、指责以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝的巴勒斯坦学者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/hebrew-university-suspends-palestinian-scholar-who-denied-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018e-3350-d5ad-addf-7f5130b60000</link><description>Nadera Shalhoub-Kevorkian教授分发了一份指责以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝的请愿书，她被要求离职但遭到拒绝，导致她被大学停职。该大学领导层对她的言论和活动表示“遗憾和羞耻”</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 19:32:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/hebrew-university-suspends-palestinian-scholar-who-denied-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018e-3350-d5ad-addf-7f5130b60000</guid></item><item><title>美国《全球威胁报告》向以色列和内塔尼亚胡发出了严厉的信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/u-s-worldwide-threats-report-says-what-biden-wont-about-gaza-war-and-netanyahu/0000018e-3379-de79-a78f-337d9a640000</link><description>国家情报总监的年度报告应该毫无疑问地表明美国认为以色列对哈马斯的战争执行得有多好，以及它对内塔尼亚胡政府的生存能力的看法</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 19:00:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/u-s-worldwide-threats-report-says-what-biden-wont-about-gaza-war-and-netanyahu/0000018e-3379-de79-a78f-337d9a640000</guid></item><item><title>萨尔解散与甘茨的联盟，要求在加沙政策发生冲突时加入战时内阁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/saar-dissolves-alliance-with-gantz-demands-joining-war-cabinet-amid-clash-on-gaza-policy/0000018e-33eb-de79-a78f-33ef1da60000</link><description>萨尔引用了加沙五人战时内阁领导的政策来证明自己的决定是正确的。他呼吁加大对哈马斯的军事压力，暗示与中间派部长甘茨和艾森科特的立场存在分歧</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 18:54:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/saar-dissolves-alliance-with-gantz-demands-joining-war-cabinet-amid-clash-on-gaza-policy/0000018e-33eb-de79-a78f-33ef1da60000</guid></item><item><title>无名，戴着镣铐：以色列道德委员会审查加沙被拘留者的医疗情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/nameless-shackled-blindfolded-medical-treatment-of-detainees-from-gaza-examined/0000018e-327a-d5ad-addf-7e7bca660000</link><description>人权医生组织称以色列军事医疗院的条件——病人一直被戴上镣铐并蒙住眼睛——是“酷刑”</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 17:35:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/nameless-shackled-blindfolded-medical-treatment-of-detainees-from-gaza-examined/0000018e-327a-d5ad-addf-7e7bca660000</guid></item><item><title>新研究显示，可可出人意料地以惊人的速度征服了史前美洲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/cocoa-always-was-though-not-sure-always-will-be/0000018e-3322-d606-a5ff-7fb706420000</link><description>可可豆于 5,300 多年前在亚马逊地区被驯化，突然之间，杂交品种在整个南美洲北部和中美洲涌现</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 17:10:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/cocoa-always-was-though-not-sure-always-will-be/0000018e-3322-d606-a5ff-7fb706420000</guid></item><item><title>应德国要求，以色列暂时将68名巴勒斯坦孤儿从拉法撤离至约旦河西岸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/israel-temporarily-evacuates-68-orphans-from-rafah-to-west-bank-at-germanys-request/0000018e-3396-da0e-a78f-ffbeccf30000</link><description>德国驻特拉维夫大使馆表示，疏散的目的是立即使孩子们脱离“严重”危险，并且是暂时的，并不是永久搬迁。以色列国防军是在以色列政府的指示下进行此次行动的</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 17:08:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/israel-temporarily-evacuates-68-orphans-from-rafah-to-west-bank-at-germanys-request/0000018e-3396-da0e-a78f-ffbeccf30000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 158 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-158/0000018e-337e-da0e-a78f-ff7e55a60001</link><description>多哈和开罗的停火谈判仍在继续，但卡塔尔外交部表示，“情况很复杂” ■ 黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射了 100 多枚火箭弹 ■ 据报道，拜登正在考虑对以色列提供进一步的军事援助，条件是这些援助是否会携带在加沙拉法发动大规模攻势 ■ 战争开始 158 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 17:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-158/0000018e-337e-da0e-a78f-ff7e55a60001</guid></item><item><title>他们的亲人在哈马斯囚禁期间被杀。他们为拯救他人的生命而奋斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/their-loved-ones-were-killed-in-captivity-they-call-to-save-others/0000018e-2f41-dcb3-a58f-efc5ddf90000</link><description>他们被绑架的亲属在加沙被杀。但只要还有其他以色列人仍被囚禁，他们的战斗就没有结束</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 16:45:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/their-loved-ones-were-killed-in-captivity-they-call-to-save-others/0000018e-2f41-dcb3-a58f-efc5ddf90000</guid></item></channel></rss>